high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the section of counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the large golden spoon off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the golden spoon in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean golden spoon.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Put the clean golden spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean golden spoon on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Wash the ladle in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Place the ladle on the counter, to the right of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean ladle on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and face the counter with the toaster on top.
Pick up the ice cream scoop from the counter.
Move a few steps to the sink on your left.
Wash the ice cream scoop in the sink.
Turn left and move to the counter top to the right of the dishwasher.
Set the ice cream scoop on the counter to the left of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put the clean ice cream scoop on the counter.
